  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Formula 1 Sensation is an arcade-style racing game for the NES. Race against up to eleven other rivals in either a single race or the grand prix! Each race unfolds at blistering speeds on tracks influenced by the 1992 Formula One season. Players have access to a wide assortment of customizations to optimize their vehicles.",
